{"tid":1768911,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人知一個月前嘅今日係咩日子？","createTime":"2019-12-04T12:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T06:31:16.000Z","uid":307619,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7cfbacad8dc3a3bb6150ae0cac9cbf0f15a66b","tid":1768911,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"你仲記得嗎？<br />\n11月4號，係梓樂墜下嘅一個晚上。<br />\n當日墜下的，有機會係妳同你。<br />\n剛巧，墜下嘅係另一位大好青年。<br />\n<br />\n一個月，梓樂仍然死得不明不白。<br />\n佢沒辦法出席大學畢業禮，<br />\n就已經要面對人生嘅畢業禮。<br />\n<br />\n答應佢，<br />\n我地會永遠記住呢個名字：周梓樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dd1D4y4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDd1D4y4.png&h=6bfe6ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7989cf999760f102512021cabc4a7e135f57a557","tid":1768911,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"永遠不要忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1f17089664038ad68ed5a800902f51c87ffb7b","tid":1768911,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"88efc942da39770e5549c01a9d31109e9eac832e","tid":1768911,"uid":300791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d99e060666d19b34124d0a1b3813453c1a2542","tid":1768911,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:28:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1538e56289843ced810357540ef561b32d874261","tid":1768911,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"梓樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd4433560ea6268ee93d2324b77626d6e6540c1","tid":1768911,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"<